{"body": "@fxn You are right. But those chdir calls are required because `find_executable_in_parent_path` doesn't return the full path of executable. It just returns `script/rails` or `bin/rails`.\r\n\r\nBut here it returns full path to executable so we can directly do `exec RUBY, exe, *ARGV` instead of again checking for `cwd == Dir.pwd` and recursing.\r\n\r\nInfact, we can drop cwd as it will not be used now.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/16160124", "created_at": "2013-04-10T07:50:57Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/10157#issuecomment-16160124", "updated_at": "2013-04-10T07:50:57Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 10157, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/prathamesh-sonpatki", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/1b0973b64704738dbc8ce24d8382bb1f?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F10a7864f54092aa82b4a41d2f0ec370c.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/received_events", "gravatar_id": "1b0973b64704738dbc8ce24d8382bb1f", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "prathamesh-sonpatki", "type": "User", "id": 621238, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523cf300bd354364b900372d"}, "id": 16160124, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/10157"}
